title: AUG/SEPT Move In - Beautiful 4 bedroom townhouse
posting_body: ['NOT APPROVED FOR SECTION 8', 'TOURING:', 'You return the Tenant Scoring sheet to set a tour.', '(If you have a voucher you must include a photo of that with your Tenant Scoring sheet.)', ' Please provide your email address so we can send you the simple form and all the other info on the association.', ' Thank you.', 'QUICK QUESTION?', ' Leslie Dahlen, Realtor.', 'show contact info', 'Features:', 'GORGEOUS KITCHEN with open and bright living area with newer appliances.', 'CORNER UNIT', 'LARGE DECK off dining area/kitchen', 'LOCATION:', 'Great Savage location, close to Hy-Vee, parks and freeways.', 'STYLE: Many updates.', 'GARAGE: 2 Car attached', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Air Conditioning.', 'SUPER CLEAN', 'PET FRIENDLY.', 'PET RENT OF $25/MO/PET', 'Rent for 1 year: $2,490/month plus all utilities', 'Utilities per current tenant - yours may vary: Elect.', '$60-$100, Gas $70-$100.', 'City water/ Sewer $75', 'Association Dues are paid by Landlord and include snow removal, lawn maintenance.', 'Security Deposit with Perfect Background equal to rent.', 'Less than perfect background?', "Please review our Tenant Scoring Sheet to determine if you will need a higher security deposit and/or last month's rent.", 'Pets: $500 Sec.', 'Dep.', 'per pet.', '$7,470 min monthly income must be documented.', '(Sec. 8 voucher offsets income requirements on amount county covers).', 'All applicants must fit the tenant acceptance policy regardless of race, age, household composition, etc.', 'We will email you the Tenant Scoring Sheet', 'to return prior to us scheduling your tour.', 'FAIR HOUSING LANDLORD']
